{
  "design_notes": "A well-paced medium chart that scales up nicely. Intro uses steady quarter and eighth note taps with comfortable holds to match vocal phrasing. The build-up slightly increases density before introducing stream-like movements and jumps on accents during the first drop. A brief transition section offers a physical breather before launching into the main peak-energy drop, which features moderate movement, crossovers, and holds. Outro tapers off with sparse grid-based notes to guide the player to the end of the track.",
